  "instructions": [
    "Bring the vegetable broth to a boil in a large pot.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "Add the coconut milk, baking powder, and nuka-pickle to the pot.",
    "Stir to combine and cook for an additional 5 minutes.",
    "Add the tofu, shiitake mushrooms, and bok choy to the pot.",
    "Cook for 3-4 minutes or until the vegetables are tender.",
    "Taste and adjust the seasoning with fish sauce and soy sauce if desired.",
    "Divide the cooked noodles among four bowls.",
    "Ladle the warm noodle broth over the noodles and garnish with fresh basil.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
